== 踢球風格 ==
保特是典型的「禁區殺手」球員，高入球率是其關鍵特徵，自從加盟[[流浪者足球俱乐部|格拉斯哥流浪]]後，他平均每3場賽事射入2球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/scotland/article6851535.ece |title=Give Kris Boyd his chance against Seville |publisher=''The Times Online'' |date=28 September 2009 |accessdate=2009-10-24}}</ref>，有很多入球更是他於後補上陣時射入，使到他的場均入球比率更加驚人<ref name="broadfoot-october">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.heraldscotland.com/sport/spl/rangers/kris-boyd-slips-further-down-ibrox-bill-despite-unexpected-old-firm-cameo-1.924327 |title=Kris Boyd slips further down Ibrox bill despite unexpected Old Firm cameo |publisher=''The Herald'' |date=2009-10-06 |accessdate=2009-10-24 |archive-date=2009-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091012122721/http://www.heraldscotland.com/sport/spl/rangers/kris-boyd-slips-further-down-ibrox-bill-despite-unexpected-old-firm-cameo-1.924327 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保特喜歡逗留在禁區內與敵衛周旋<ref name="stein">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://sport.scotsman.com/top-stories/Stein-backs-poacher-striker-to.2689145.jp |title=Stein backs 'poacher' striker to be a success |publisher=''The Scotsman'' |date= |accessdate=2009-10-24 |archive-date=2011-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110617052650/http://sport.scotsman.com/top-stories/Stein-backs-poacher-striker-to.2689145.jp |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[阿歷斯·麥利殊|阿歷斯·麥利殊]]（Alex McLeish）認為他的入球能力可以媲美[[雅利·麥哥斯|雅利·麥哥斯]]（Ally McCoist）<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-477203/Boyds-nose-goal-reminds-Eck-Coisty.html |title=Boyd's nose for goal reminds Eck of Coisty |publisher=''Daily Mail Online'' |date=2007-08-23 |accessdate=2009-10-24 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304140104/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-477203/Boyds-nose-goal-reminds-Eck-Coisty.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

但當他沒法取得入球時，其對球隊的整體貢獻常被質疑<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.heraldscotland.com/boyd-is-determined-to-prove-critics-wrong-once-again-1.862535 |title=Boyd is determined to prove critics wrong once again |publisher=''The Herald'' |date=2007-08-04 |accessdate=2009-10-24 |archive-date=2009-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091104231406/http://www.heraldscotland.com/boyd-is-determined-to-prove-critics-wrong-once-again-1.862535 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，格拉斯哥流浪領隊[[禾達·史密夫|禾達·史密夫]]由於其對球隊的團隊演出缺乏貢獻而間中棄用他<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url = http://www.heraldscotland.com/smith-ponders-the-enigma-that-is-kris-boyd-1.881178 |title=Smith ponders the enigma that is Kris Boyd |publisher=''The Herald'' |date=2008-05-26 |accessdate=2009-10-24}}</ref>，在禾達·史密夫慣常採用的[[足球陣式|4-5-1陣式]]，保特並非單箭頭的合適人選<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/sport/football/scotland/article2767839.ece |title=Mystery of Kris Boyd’s striking lack of chances at Rangers |publisher=''The Times Online'' |date=30 October 2007 |accessdate=2009-10-24}}</ref>。球評家亦指出，他的風格依賴隊中其他隊友的良好支援，如在早年格拉斯哥流浪財雄勢大時，可負擔聘用高質球員支援前線球員，保特的演出容或更具效率<ref name="broadfoot-october" />。

